ately.\n- The attribute table and parts table both align with the source material.\n- The three RST sections (コードサンプル, 仕様, 内部構造・改修時の留意点) correspond correctly to the three sections in the knowledge file.\n- Checking the hints - s1 includes field_base, field_text, field_checkbox; s2 covers all attribute names; s3 references base.tag and nablarch.less - all appropriate.\n- The knowledge file appears to accurately represent the source content without critical issues.\n- One minor note: the source has a typo (\"実装の実装\") that the knowledge file corrects to \"実装で使用するテンプレート\", which is acceptable. The legend omits the × symbol for invalid attributes, but since none are actually used in the table, this doesn't impact anything.\n- Overall, the knowledge file looks clean and ready.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13370,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":13370,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cfd0b364-f909-42ff-a9d5-a9d56235052b","uuid":"b4f3abbd-0ad4-4b1d-a7d7-5516ddea9d50"}
